Package bacnet.scripts.listeriomics.srna

Class SrnaTables

java.lang.Object
bacnet.scripts.listeriomics.srna.SrnaTables
public class SrnaTables extends Object
Include a list of Methods to read every Table containing Small RNAs in Listeria
For each it reads the Table and create a List of Srna
